        This object represents a VCF or vCard QR Code. Use null if you don't want to specify an option. Styling options can be set with the setter functions of the upper class.
        Parameters:
        name - Name of this code for the tag.
        latitude - Latitude.
        altitude - Altitude.
        longitude - Longitude.
